OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FSome adults in are waiting three years
OL,7,Ffor an assessment, with more than 700
OL,8,Fnow on the list for an appointment.
OL,10,FThe backlog could worsen as around 140
OL,11,Fyoung people are currently being
OL,12,Flooked after by the island's Child and
OL,13,FAdolescent Mental Health Service
OL,14,F(CAMHS) and will eventually need to be
OL,15,Fmoved into the adult service.
OL,17,FAttention Deficit Hyperactivity
OL,18,FDisorder or ADHD can affect someone's
OL,19,Fbehaviour in different ways, such as
OL,20,Fmaking it difficult to focus, follow
OL,21,Finstructions and cope with stress.
