OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FJersey's Director of Mental Health,
OL,7,FAndy Weir, says the long wait is down
OL,8,Fto a rise in demand without the number
OL,9,Fof staff to meet it.
OL,11,FOne specialist consultant psychiatrist
OL,12,Fis currently doing all of the
OL,13,Fassessments and repeat prescriptions.
OL,15,FHe explained: "It's not fair, it's not
OL,16,FOK for people to be waiting such a
OL,17,Flong time for a diagnostic assessment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
