OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,F"We've seen a significant increase in
OL,7,Freferrals and activity over the last
OL,8,Fcouple of years. We've not had the
OL,9,Fassociated growth of the service,
OL,10,Fparticularly because we've not been
OL,11,Fable to achieve the staff to get with
OL,12,Fspecialist skills and expertise in
OL,13,Fthis area.
OL,15,F"At the moment, if you were added
OL,16,Ftoday, it's three years based upon the
OL,17,Fnumber of assessments that we do each
OL,18,Fmonth."
