OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FRepeat prescriptions compound the
OL,7,Fproblem as they have to be signed off
OL,8,Fby a specialist in Jersey, unlike in
OL,9,Fthe UK where a GP can issue them.
OL,11,FThis means the on-island specialist
OL,12,Fpsychiatrist is prescribing for 220
OL,13,Fpeople every four weeks which takes up
OL,14,Fmost of their time - something the
OL,15,Fdepartment wants to change.
