OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FMr Weir added: "We've looked at non-
OL,7,Fmedical prescribing so that we could
OL,8,Fhave someone who isn't a psychiatrist
OL,9,Fbut is a specialist in mental health
OL,10,Fdoing the prescribing, but we've not
OL,11,Fmanaged to find anyone who's able to
OL,12,For wanting to do that at the moment."
OL,14,FTo tackle the backlog, he admits the
OL,15,Fdepartment has discussed the idea of
OL,16,Fclosing the waiting list for new adult
OL,17,Freferrals, except in emergency cases.
