OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FMr Weir explained: "I think we have to
OL,7,Fthink about if people are being
OL,8,Freferred to a service where they're
OL,9,Fnot being seen for potentially three
OL,10,Fyears, is that fair? Is that
OL,11,Freasonable? But there isn't an
OL,12,Falternative here and we have an unmet
OL,13,Fneed."
OL,15,FThis news comes as no surprise to
OL,16,FRachel Tippett, the founder of ADHD
OL,17,FJersey, a not for profit organisation.
