OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FShe says she warned the government two
OL,7,Fyears ago that referrals were going to
OL,8,Fincrease: "At the time, the expression
OL,9,FI used was 'let's shut the gate before
OL,10,Fthe horse bolts', but now the horse
OL,11,Fhas already bolted.
OL,13,F"There are problems with the ADHD
OL,14,Fdiagnosis, there are problems with
OL,15,Fprescriptions, there are problems with
OL,16,Fgetting the medication. There is no
OL,17,Fafter support, it's just a complete
OL,18,Fshambles.
