OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,F"ADHD is 80% hereditary. It's really
OL,7,Fgood how much work CAMHS is doing but
OL,8,Fwe need to realise that when you have
OL,9,Fsomething that is so highly
OL,10,Fhereditary, the adults also need to be
OL,11,Flooked after because these are the
OL,12,Fadults who are parenting our children
OL,13,Fwith ADHD."
OL,15,FChildren are also facing a long wait
OL,16,Ffor an ADHD assessment.
