OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,FNina Lodwick-Campbell's youngest son
OL,7,Fwas diagnosed with the condition in
OL,8,FSeptember 2023 but admits the four-
OL,9,Fyear journey has been tough on the
OL,10,Fentire family: "I knew my child was
OL,11,Fdifferent at 18 months and we got the
OL,12,Fdiagnosis just weeks before he turned
OL,13,Fsix years old.
OL,15,F"I don't know how I got through those
OL,16,Ffour years. It was crises on a daily
OL,17,Fbasis.
OL,19,F"There are still people who think it's
OL,20,Fjust behaviour. My child would climb
OL,21,Fonto the car or climb buildings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
