OL,3,CADHD care a 'complete shambles' as
OL,4,Cadults wait three years to be diagnosed
OL,6,F"It's not just down to parenting, it's
OL,7,Fnot just down to styles of parenting.
OL,8,FTheir brain works differently and we
OL,9,Fneed to be able to help them. We don't
OL,10,Fall fit in the same square."
OL,12,FThree days after receiving the
OL,13,Fdiagnosis, Nina's son went from
OL,14,Freceiving 15 minutes of one-on-one
OL,15,Fsupport in school to 90 minutes each
OL,16,Fmorning.
